>>LISA: You can see
how many layers there

00:09:42.650 --> 00:09:44.240 align:middle line:90%
were in that particular clip.

00:09:44.240 --> 00:09:47.400 align:middle line:84%
You have touched on so
many things in this DVD.

00:09:47.400 --> 00:09:49.220 align:middle line:84%
So, I want to start
out in the beginning

00:09:49.220 --> 00:09:53.350 align:middle line:84%
where you talked about the
energy, the torus energy,

00:09:53.350 --> 00:09:58.010 align:middle line:84%
