the corporations.

00:32:09.420 --> 00:32:11.160 align:middle line:84%
As I followed the
money, I've learned

00:32:11.160 --> 00:32:14.570 align:middle line:84%
that almost everything I
once believed about money

00:32:14.570 --> 00:32:16.460 align:middle line:90%
is simply not true.

00:32:16.460 --> 00:32:20.410 align:middle line:84%
-It's interesting how
few questions we actually

00:32:20.410 --> 00:32:25.040 align:middle line:84%
ask about very everyday things,
