00:32:30.920 --> 00:32:33.620 align:middle line:84%
You see, most people
live their lives

00:32:33.620 --> 00:32:37.300 align:middle line:84%
based on a kind of vague
image of what happens.

00:32:37.300 --> 00:32:40.870 align:middle line:84%
