00:32:43.800 --> 00:32:45.840 align:middle line:90%
That's all they do.

00:32:45.840 --> 00:32:50.460 align:middle line:84%
They don't mint any coins,
they don't print any money,

00:32:50.460 --> 00:32:53.090 align:middle line:84%
they don't move any
precious metal anywhere.

00:32:53.090 --> 00:32:55.240 align:middle line:84%
They just put 50,000
pounds into your account

00:32:55.240 --> 00:32:56.430 align:middle line:90%
on a computer screen.

00:32:56.430 --> 00:33:00.420 align:middle line:84%
From that moment, you
start paying interest

00:33:00.420 --> 00:33:06.370 align:middle line:84%
