00:33:45.850 --> 00:33:50.620 align:middle line:84%
It's just that this banking
scam, this centralized fiat

00:33:50.620 --> 00:33:52.740 align:middle line:84%
money, which means making
up money out of nothing,

00:33:52.740 --> 00:33:55.480 align:middle line:84%
