01:13:48.390 --> 01:13:50.250 align:middle line:90%
of the liberty perspective.

01:13:50.250 --> 01:13:52.870 align:middle line:84%
While stage one has a
lot of the compassion

01:13:52.870 --> 01:13:56.170 align:middle line:84%
typically associated with
a liberal democrat agenda,

01:13:56.170 --> 01:13:58.840 align:middle line:84%
stage two reflects
much of the wisdom

01:13:58.840 --> 01:14:02.150 align:middle line:84%
of the traditional
conservative worldview.

01:14:02.150 --> 01:14:04.550 align:middle line:84%
In stage two, we shrink
government's role

01:14:04.550 --> 01:14:07.440 align:middle line:84%
to protect individual
liberty and stewarding

01:14:07.440 --> 01:14:10.450 align:middle line:84%
things we share in
common, like ecosystems,

01:14:10.450 --> 01:14:12.075 align:middle line:84%
and the airwaves we
use to communicate.

01:14:12.075 --> 01:14:15.370 align:middle line:90%


01:14:15.370 --> 01:14:19.940 align:middle line:84%
As the system gains integrity
and we move to sound currency,

01:14:19.940 --> 01:14:21.520 align:middle line:84%
people will have
enough money to have

01:14:21.520 --> 01:14:25.540 align:middle line:84%
more control over everything
that affects them.

01:14:25.540 --> 01:14:28.390 align:middle line:84%
Stage three grows out of
the increasing freedom

01:14:28.390 --> 01:14:30.960 align:middle line:84%
that people gain in
stages one and two

01:14:30.960 --> 01:14:34.530 align:middle line:84%
as they have more
money and more time.

01:14:34.530 --> 01:14:37.200 align:middle line:84%
There is no involuntary
tax, and therefore,

01:14:37.200 --> 01:14:39.580 align:middle line:90%
no involuntary governance.

01:14:39.580 --> 01:14:41.960 align:middle line:90%
There's no monopoly on force.

01:14:41.960 --> 01:14:45.660 align:middle line:90%
There are rules but no rulers.

01:14:45.660 --> 01:14:47.980 align:middle line:84%
Rigorously protecting
individual rights

01:14:47.980 --> 01:14:51.900 align:middle line:84%
turns out to be key for
honoring our interdependence.

01:14:51.900 --> 01:14:57.000 align:middle line:84%
We can be distinct and
unified at the same time.

01:14:57.000 --> 01:14:59.890 align:middle line:84%
As Utopian as this
can sound at first,

01:14:59.890 --> 01:15:02.830 align:middle line:84%
I've been thrilled to see how
much practical thinking has

01:15:02.830 --> 01:15:04.990 align:middle line:84%
been done to deal
with tough issues

01:15:04.990 --> 01:15:10.420 align:middle line:84%
like health care,
crime, and education.

01:15:10.420 --> 01:15:12.760 align:middle line:84%
These three stages
validate the best

01:15:12.760 --> 01:15:15.230 align:middle line:84%
of both the liberal and
conservative perspectives

01:15:15.230 --> 01:15:17.670 align:middle line:84%
that have divided
us for so long,

01:15:17.670 --> 01:15:22.450 align:middle line:84%
and then reconcile them at a
new level around non-violation,

01:15:22.450 --> 01:15:26.290 align:middle line:90%
a core ethic we all share.

01:15:26.290 --> 01:15:29.020 align:middle line:84%
Stage three honors
human incentive

01:15:29.020 --> 01:15:33.100 align:middle line:84%
and finally includes the rights
of not just many, not just

01:15:33.100 --> 01:15:34.883 align:middle line:90%
most, but everyone.

